Revision history

1.1     Pending release

        - On OS X, expand `~` to the actual `$HOME` path in SQLite DB connection string
          https://github.com/evernote/serge/issues/1

        - Accept multiple `message` entries in append_hint_message plugin
          https://github.com/evernote/serge/issues/2

        - Require JSON::XS
          https://github.com/evernote/serge/issues/3

        - Make serge and tools fine their libs when they are symlinked
          https://github.com/evernote/serge/issues/4

        - Fixed: Uppercase letters in language names are unsupported
          https://github.com/evernote/serge/issues/5

        - Accept multiple `command` entries in run_command plugin
          https://github.com/evernote/serge/issues/6

        - parse_android plugin now supports `serge import` mode
          (generates string keys for alignment)
          https://github.com/evernote/serge/issues/7

        - parse_pot plugin now supports `serge import` mode
          (generates string keys for alignment)
          https://github.com/evernote/serge/issues/8

        - Added support for %OUTFILE% and %OUTPATH% macros in `run_command` plugin;
          other macros like %FILE% now work consistently with the rest of the config code

        - Fixed some tests due to broken source files

        - Fixed typos in embedded documentation

1.0     October 15, 2012

        * Code published on GitHub *
